    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/22707c87c063c77482342556bd29e7ba.poster.avif?t=1726467707\" width=554 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/22707c87c063c77482342556bd29e7ba.webm?t=1726467707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/22707c87c063c77482342556bd29e7ba.mp4?t=1726467707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新的大地图多人射击游戏</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/307bde164c115019b55144ec8d5cc4c7.webp?t=1726467707\" width=12 height=13 /></span>目标很简单：夺回地球的控制权。<br>在《Second Extinction》中，你可以与最多两名好友并肩作战，一起对抗变异了的各种恐龙。单人玩家请注意：二次灭绝 Second Extinction 鼓励团队协同作战，唯有强者方可生存。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/7d24ddd783da528c2007417b9ee2a850.avif?t=1726467707\" width=640 height=188 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抢先体验只是开始</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/307bde164c115019b55144ec8d5cc4c7.webp?t=1726467707\" width=12 height=13 /></span>抢先体验的目标也很简单：与我们的社区合作，<br>尽力制作出最好的游戏。<br>我们希望能清晰地听到你们的反馈，我们也有意使我们的社区<br>成为开发过程中关键的一部分。<br>即便这么说，还是有大量内容等着您在首日进行探索：6名英雄，<br>11件武器（各自有5个等级可升）以及6项任务——此外还有一些特殊支线任务，遍布在大地图<br>的多个地区。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/5f022d576480e121b1e97990152d1b6e.avif?t=1726467707\" width=640 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入征战历程，塑造未来</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/307bde164c115019b55144ec8d5cc4c7.webp?t=1726467707\" width=12 height=13 /></span>我们的信条就是玩家赢得战斗即是社区赢得战斗。没有什么能比<br>我们的征战历程特色更能体现这一点了。<br>我们的大地图上每个地区都有各自的威胁等级。而这些威胁等级可以<br>藉由足够的玩家成功完成任务和活动来降低。但是恐龙们也不会闲着，它们会把重点放在你们照顾不到的地方。<br>社区每周都可以看到自己的劳动成果，又或者<br>体会到无为带来的后果。如果任由威胁等级失控，<br>等待您的就是极其困难的突发事件。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/2c453ce45f3165d95e0258c272ee8c8b.poster.avif?t=1726467707\" width=554 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/2c453ce45f3165d95e0258c272ee8c8b.webm?t=1726467707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/2c453ce45f3165d95e0258c272ee8c8b.mp4?t=1726467707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024380/extras/307bde164c115019b55144ec8d5cc4c7.webp?t=1726467707\" width=12 height=13 /></span>游玩二次灭绝 Second Extinction 可不只是随意选择了又一款合作射击游戏。<br>您将会和我们共享这份体验并加入到我们的旅程中来。您的每一份反馈<br>以及游玩的每一场任务都至关重要。那么您还等什么？收复<br>地球的战斗由此开始。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
